Product Requirements Document (PRD): Enterprise Employee Travel & Expense Management System
1. Project Overview
The Enterprise Employee Travel & Expense Management System is a centralized platform designed to streamline and automate corporate travel requests, approval workflows, expense claim submissions, and reimbursement processing for organizations with 10,000+ employees across multiple locations.
The system eliminates manual processes involving emails, spreadsheets, phone calls, and paper documents by providing a unified digital solution that improves transparency, compliance, operational efficiency, and employee experience.

2. Project Scope
2.1 In Scope
Employee Management
* Employee onboarding and profile management.
* Secure authentication and role-based access control.
* Employee, Manager, Finance, and Admin roles.
Travel Request Management
* Travel request creation and submission.
* Travel itinerary management.
* Budget estimation and travel purpose tracking.
* Travel request modification and cancellation.
Approval Workflow
* Single and multi-level approval workflows.
* Approval comments and feedback.
* Approval history and audit trail.
* Automated approval notifications.
Travel Booking Management
* Flight, train, hotel, and transportation requests.
* Booking status tracking.
* Travel schedule management.
* Travel itinerary generation.
Expense Management
* Expense claim creation and submission.
* Receipt upload and document management.
* Expense categorization.
* Policy validation and compliance checks.
Reimbursement Management
* Finance approval workflows.
* Reimbursement processing and tracking.
* Payment status monitoring.
* Historical reimbursement records.
Reporting & Analytics
* Travel spending reports.
* Expense trend analysis.
* Department-wise cost reporting.
* Executive dashboards.
Deployment & Infrastructure
* Docker-based deployment.
* Database persistence.
* API documentation.
* Automated testing.

2.2 Out of Scope
Travel Booking Integrations
* Direct integration with airline, railway, or hotel booking providers.
Corporate Credit Card Processing
* Automated corporate card reconciliation.
Payroll Integration
* Direct salary processing and payroll deductions.
Native Mobile Applications
* Separate iOS and Android applications.
* Responsive web application only.
International Tax Compliance
* Country-specific tax calculations and compliance regulations.
AI-Based Travel Recommendations
* Automated destination suggestions or travel optimization.
Third-Party ERP Integration
* SAP, Oracle ERP, or Workday integration in the initial release.

